                },
                {
                    "start": 1487,
                    "end": 1491,
                    "text": "[16]",
                    "ref_id": "BIBREF15"
                }
            ],
            "ref_spans": [],
            "section": ""
        },
        {
            "text": "The situation of the COVID-19 outbreak is rapidly evolving, with uncertain clinical and physiopathological profiles. However, the first case reports indicate that COVID-19 has important effects on the heart and the vessels, which should be known by the cardiovascular community. ",
